{"title":"求Z 字形变换后的字符串","slug":"2019090702","date":"2019-09-07T14:32:23.000Z","updated":"2019-09-07T12:51:23.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019090702.json","excerpt":"题目将一个给定字符串根据给定的行数，以从上往下、从左到右进行 Z 字形排列。比如输入字符串为 “LEETCODEISHIRING” 行数为 3 时，排列如下：<br> [Figure] 请你实现这个将字符串进行指定行数变换的函数：","covers":["https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf89e92c8167b4e02b30824935decad86s.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H69b9aa530da4476e8c0b89e79384d50fW.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H53642d413a5d4eb6967502a421b88f37E.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf245a3a4eadd4e3ba8d841a05fa26371w.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hc81370f06e72410a9529beff4315eaf7u.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"题目\"><a href=\"#题目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目\"></a>题目</h2><p>将一个给定字符串根据给定的行数，以从上往下、从左到右进行 Z 字形排列。</p>\n<p>比如输入字符串为 “LEETCODEISHIRING” 行数为 3 时，排列如下：<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf89e92c8167b4e02b30824935decad86s.png\"></p>\n<p>之后，你的输出需要从左往右逐行读取，产生出一个新的字符串，比如：”LCIRETOESIIGEDHN”。<br>请你实现这个将字符串进行指定行数变换的函数：</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"示例\"></a>示例</h2><p>示例1：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>输入: s = “LEETCODEISHIRING”, numRows = 3<br>输出: “LCIRETOESIIGEDHN”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>示例2：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>输入: s = “LEETCODEISHIRING”, numRows = 4<br>输出: “LDREOEIIECIHNTSG”<br>解释:<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H69b9aa530da4476e8c0b89e79384d50fW.png\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><h3 id=\"旧版本\"><a href=\"#旧版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"旧版本\"></a>旧版本</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title\">convert</span><span class=\"params\">(String s, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> numRows)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> len=s.length();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> rowLen=numRows;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> colLen=len;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(rowLen&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            colLen=((<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>) Math.ceil((<span class=\"keyword\">double</span>)len / (<span class=\"number\">2</span> * (numRows - <span class=\"number\">1</span>))))*(numRows-<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        String[][] arr=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> String[rowLen][colLen];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> indexCol=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> indexRow=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> index=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(index&lt;len)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(indexRow=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;indexRow&lt;rowLen&amp;&amp;index&lt;len;indexRow++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                arr[indexRow][indexCol]= String.valueOf(s.charAt(index++));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(indexRow--;indexRow&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>&amp;&amp;index&lt;len;)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        arr[--indexRow][++indexCol]=String.valueOf(s.charAt(index++));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            indexRow--;indexCol++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        StringBuffer sb=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> StringBuffer();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;rowLen;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;j&lt;colLen;j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(arr[i][j]!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    sb.append(arr[i][j]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> sb.toString();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"新版本（推荐）\"><a href=\"#新版本（推荐）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新版本（推荐）\"></a>新版本（推荐）</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title\">convert</span><span class=\"params\">(String s, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> numRows)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> len=s.length();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> groupLen=<span class=\"number\">2</span>*(numRows-<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(numRows==<span class=\"number\">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                groupLen=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> groupNum=(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>) Math.ceil((<span class=\"keyword\">double</span>)len/groupLen);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">            StringBuffer sb=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> StringBuffer();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;numRows;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> l=groupLen-i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;j&lt;groupNum;j++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(j*groupLen+i&lt;len)</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    sb.append(s.charAt(j*groupLen+i));</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(l&lt;groupLen&amp;&amp;l-i&gt;<span class=\"number\">0</span>&amp;&amp;j*groupLen+l&lt;len) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        sb.append(s.charAt(j*groupLen+l));</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> sb.toString();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"结果\"><a href=\"#结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"结果\"></a>结果</h2><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H53642d413a5d4eb6967502a421b88f37E.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>9月7日：<br>我是谁？我在哪？（代码太迷，复杂，想看的可以先看一下，明天会优化一下代码，对算法进行补充）</p>\n<hr>\n<p>9月9日更新：<br>新的方法思想和旧的方法有着完全不同的思路，这也是我在刚完成旧方法时才想出来的，可以看到执行用时和内存消耗分别对比旧的版本都发生了质的变化！</p>\n<p>旧方法的执行步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>以每个Z字型的前两笔（即V型）作为一组，分组，根据每组的数量，求出一个长宽尽可能小的二维数组。</li>\n<li>定义i，j下标，根据V字的特性，遍历使二维数组逐个填充，直至遍历完毕。</li>\n<li>横向遍历，如果该项有值则取值存至新的字符串。</li>\n<li>遍历结束，得到正解。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>旧方法存在的问题：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>遍历V字型填充时，下标位置难以确定。</strong> 这也是我最头疼的问题，难点在于对于特殊情况的处理，当numsRow为1时，会造成数组越界，虽然之后调好了却依然花费了很大的经历。</li>\n<li><strong>先遍历填充，再取值带来的复杂度问题</strong> 虽然说还是完成题目，但是时间复杂度却很高，这也是我为什么要使用新方法的原因。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>新方法的执行步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>以每个Z字型的前两笔（即V型）作为一组，分组，得到组数和每组数字的数量</li>\n<li>直接开始取值，遍历numRows次，第一次拿每组的第一行的值即每组的第一项（每组的最后一项在每组的第二行），这样第一次遍历结束后暂时的数组为[组1的第1项，组2的第1项…组n的第1项]，第二次遍历取每组的第二行，这样第二次遍历结束后暂时的数组为[组1的第1项，组2的第1项…组n的第1项，组1的第2项，组1的第组长度-1项，组2的第2项，组2的第组长度-1项…组n的第2项，组n的第组长度-1项，]，以此类推直到最后一次，最后一次因为每组的最后一行同样只有一个值，所以只取一个值。<strong>简单总结一下就是：每组的第一行和最后一行都只有一个值，其他行在遍历时收尾各取一个值</strong></li>\n<li>遍历结束，得到正解</li>\n</ol>\n<p>新方法的优点是速度快，相比之前简直是质的飞跃。缺点就是太多抽象，但也正因为如此才省去了遍历到二维数组里的时间，而改为从数组里直接拿值。</p>\n<p>提交反馈：<br>旧版本：<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf245a3a4eadd4e3ba8d841a05fa26371w.png\"></p>\n<p>新版本：<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hc81370f06e72410a9529beff4315eaf7u.png\"></p>\n","more":"<h2 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"示例\"></a>示例</h2><p>示例1：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>输入: s = “LEETCODEISHIRING”, numRows = 3<br>输出: “LCIRETOESIIGEDHN”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>示例2：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>输入: s = “LEETCODEISHIRING”, numRows = 4<br>输出: “LDREOEIIECIHNTSG”<br>解释:<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H69b9aa530da4476e8c0b89e79384d50fW.png\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><h3 id=\"旧版本\"><a href=\"#旧版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"旧版本\"></a>旧版本</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title\">convert</span><span class=\"params\">(String s, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> numRows)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> len=s.length();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> rowLen=numRows;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> colLen=len;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(rowLen&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            colLen=((<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>) Math.ceil((<span class=\"keyword\">double</span>)len / (<span class=\"number\">2</span> * (numRows - <span class=\"number\">1</span>))))*(numRows-<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        String[][] arr=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> String[rowLen][colLen];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> indexCol=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> indexRow=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> index=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(index&lt;len)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(indexRow=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;indexRow&lt;rowLen&amp;&amp;index&lt;len;indexRow++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                arr[indexRow][indexCol]= String.valueOf(s.charAt(index++));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(indexRow--;indexRow&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>&amp;&amp;index&lt;len;)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        arr[--indexRow][++indexCol]=String.valueOf(s.charAt(index++));</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            indexRow--;indexCol++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        StringBuffer sb=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> StringBuffer();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;rowLen;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;j&lt;colLen;j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(arr[i][j]!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    sb.append(arr[i][j]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> sb.toString();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"新版本（推荐）\"><a href=\"#新版本（推荐）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新版本（推荐）\"></a>新版本（推荐）</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title\">convert</span><span class=\"params\">(String s, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> numRows)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> len=s.length();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> groupLen=<span class=\"number\">2</span>*(numRows-<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(numRows==<span class=\"number\">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                groupLen=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> groupNum=(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>) Math.ceil((<span class=\"keyword\">double</span>)len/groupLen);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">            StringBuffer sb=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> StringBuffer();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;numRows;i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> l=groupLen-i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;j&lt;groupNum;j++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(j*groupLen+i&lt;len)</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    sb.append(s.charAt(j*groupLen+i));</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(l&lt;groupLen&amp;&amp;l-i&gt;<span class=\"number\">0</span>&amp;&amp;j*groupLen+l&lt;len) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        sb.append(s.charAt(j*groupLen+l));</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> sb.toString();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"结果\"><a href=\"#结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"结果\"></a>结果</h2><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H53642d413a5d4eb6967502a421b88f37E.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>9月7日：<br>我是谁？我在哪？（代码太迷，复杂，想看的可以先看一下，明天会优化一下代码，对算法进行补充）</p>\n<hr>\n<p>9月9日更新：<br>新的方法思想和旧的方法有着完全不同的思路，这也是我在刚完成旧方法时才想出来的，可以看到执行用时和内存消耗分别对比旧的版本都发生了质的变化！</p>\n<p>旧方法的执行步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>以每个Z字型的前两笔（即V型）作为一组，分组，根据每组的数量，求出一个长宽尽可能小的二维数组。</li>\n<li>定义i，j下标，根据V字的特性，遍历使二维数组逐个填充，直至遍历完毕。</li>\n<li>横向遍历，如果该项有值则取值存至新的字符串。</li>\n<li>遍历结束，得到正解。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>旧方法存在的问题：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>遍历V字型填充时，下标位置难以确定。</strong> 这也是我最头疼的问题，难点在于对于特殊情况的处理，当numsRow为1时，会造成数组越界，虽然之后调好了却依然花费了很大的经历。</li>\n<li><strong>先遍历填充，再取值带来的复杂度问题</strong> 虽然说还是完成题目，但是时间复杂度却很高，这也是我为什么要使用新方法的原因。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>新方法的执行步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>以每个Z字型的前两笔（即V型）作为一组，分组，得到组数和每组数字的数量</li>\n<li>直接开始取值，遍历numRows次，第一次拿每组的第一行的值即每组的第一项（每组的最后一项在每组的第二行），这样第一次遍历结束后暂时的数组为[组1的第1项，组2的第1项…组n的第1项]，第二次遍历取每组的第二行，这样第二次遍历结束后暂时的数组为[组1的第1项，组2的第1项…组n的第1项，组1的第2项，组1的第组长度-1项，组2的第2项，组2的第组长度-1项…组n的第2项，组n的第组长度-1项，]，以此类推直到最后一次，最后一次因为每组的最后一行同样只有一个值，所以只取一个值。<strong>简单总结一下就是：每组的第一行和最后一行都只有一个值，其他行在遍历时收尾各取一个值</strong></li>\n<li>遍历结束，得到正解</li>\n</ol>\n<p>新方法的优点是速度快，相比之前简直是质的飞跃。缺点就是太多抽象，但也正因为如此才省去了遍历到二维数组里的时间，而改为从数组里直接拿值。</p>\n<p>提交反馈：<br>旧版本：<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf245a3a4eadd4e3ba8d841a05fa26371w.png\"></p>\n<p>新版本：<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hc81370f06e72410a9529beff4315eaf7u.png\"></p>","categories":[{"name":"开发","path":"api/categories/开发.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JAVA","path":"api/tags/JAVA.json"},{"name":"算法","path":"api/tags/算法.json"}]}